Package: potytools
Title: Analysis Tools for Potyvirus Genomics and Short Linear Motifs
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R:
    person("Christina", "Muedsam", email = "70411777+MintyHybrid@users.noreply.github.com",
           role = c("aut", "cre"),
           comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0001-8488-3442"))
Description: Provides functions for potyvirus genomic analysis, including
    GenBank file parsing (no external dependencies), codon usage bias
    calculation (RSCU, ENC, CAI, GC content), host classification for
    monocot/dicot-infecting isolates, motif-flanking region extraction
    and concatenation for short-linear-motif analysis, and phylogenetic
    utilities. Designed for reproducible analysis of
    Potyviridae diversity, DNAzyme-like motif conservation, and
    horizontal gene transfer detection.
